snippet.title: Backpack Twins Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Backpack Twins is an upcoming single player game where you switch between controlling two characters in order to solve environmental puzzles and, most importantly, keep both of them alive!

Add it to your wishlist on Steam to be notified when it's out!:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1049310/Backpack_Twins/

Releasing in 2019 on Steam.
